François Tardan, MBA

Age : 64Public asset : 274,933 USDLinked companies :  NV5 Global Inc 





Summary 



Mr. François Tardan is Chairman at BIVAC International SA, Chairman at Financière Saint Germain SC, Chairman at Laboratoire Central des Industries Electriques SA, Chairman at Bureau Veritas CODDE SAS, Chairman at Bureau Veritas Operations France, Chairman at BIVAC Paraguay, Chairman at Soprefira SA, a Manager at Sedhyca SARL, a Manager at BIVAC Worldmarket BV, a Director-Finance & Director at Curtis Strauss LLP, a Director & Director-Finance at Bureau Veritas Marine, Inc., and Chief Executive Office & Founding Partner at Leitmotiv Private Equity Ltd.He is on the Board of Directors at NV5 Holdings, Inc., Bureau Veritas Consulting (Shanghai) Co., Ltd., Bureau Veritas Quality Services (Shanghai) Co., Ltd., Bureau Veritas (India) Pvt Ltd., Bureau Veritas Certification India Pvt Ltd., Bureau Veritas (Malaysia) Sdn. Bhd., Bureau Veritas CPS Sdn. Bhd., Bureau Veritas del Peru SA, Bureau Veritas Romania Controle International, Bureau Veritas Thailand Ltd., Bureau Veritas Italia Holding SpA, Bureau Veritas HK Ltd., Bureau Veritas Consumer Products Services (Hong Kong) Ltd., Bureau Veritas Maroc, Bureau Veritas Lebanon SAL, Bureau Veritas Holdings SAS, Bureau Veritas Certification Canada, Inc., Bureau Veritas (Namibia) Pty Ltd., Amdel Ltd., Amdel Holdings Pty Ltd., Amdel Holdings (Finance) Pty Ltd., Labmark Pty Ltd., Bureau Veritas UK Holdings Ltd., Bureau Veritas UK Ltd., Inspectorate Group Holdings Ltd., Inspectorate Pledgeco, Inc., Bureau Veritas (Bangladesh) Pvt Ltd., Curtis Strauss LLP, and Bureau Veritas Marine, Inc.Mr. Tardan was previously employed as Non-Executive Director by DTZ Holdings Plc, Chief Financial Officer by Bureau Veritas SA, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Fondasol, and Vice President-Corporate Development by Chantiers Modernes.He received his undergraduate degree from École des Hautes Études Commerciales de Paris, an undergraduate degree from Ecole Nationale d'Administration, and an undergraduate degree from Sciences Po.



